---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="FLIP Program · Quest Labs"
  description="FLIP is a 12-week embodied, healing-centered futures development program. Join a cohort, develop futures capacities, and practice radical foresight. Cohort 02 forming now."
>

<div class="prog-page">

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<div class="prog-hero">
  <div class="prog-hero-bg"></div>
  <p class="prog-hero-eyebrow">Futures Literacies Invitational Playground</p>
  <h1 class="prog-hero-title">FLIP</h1>
  <p class="prog-hero-subtitle">The Questor's Invitational</p>
  <p class="prog-hero-sub">A 12-week creative &amp; futures journey.<br>You're invited to meet your future Self.</p>
  <div class="prog-hero-cta">
    <a href="#waitlist" class="prog-btn prog-btn-primary">Join a Cohort →</a>
    <a href="#journey" class="prog-btn prog-btn-ghost">Explore the Arc</a>
    <a href="#tiers" class="cta-ghost">Choose Your Path</a>
  </div>
  <div class="prog-scroll-hint">
    <span>Scroll</span>
    <div class="prog-scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- ── THE PREMISE ── -->
<section id="what" class="prog-what-section">
  <div class="prog-reveal">
    <p class="prog-section-label">The Premise</p>
    <h2 class="prog-section-title">Somewhere between 2026 and 2032,<br>there is a <em>portal</em>.</h2>
    <p class="prog-section-body">
      We're crossing a threshold into the unknown...<br><br>
      ...but don't lose hope.<br><br>
      A whisper of wisdom from beyond?<br><br>
      Remember, someone built this world.<br><br>
      We're here to build a new one.<br><br>
      Over 12 weeks, a cohort of 6 brave travelers move through 12 worlds. Each week the world changes: same crew, different questions. We keep what serves our future Self and collective. We discover what we're building toward.<br><br>
      By the final session, each traveler holds a <strong class="text-bright">2032 Job Description</strong> assembled piece by piece across 12 weeks of Artist's Way practices and Sandbox Sessions.<br><br>
      Not a resume. A living document. Equal parts manifesto, methodology, and spell.
    </p>
    <div class="prog-educator-bridge">
      <p class="prog-educator-bridge__label">Teaching? Leading a school?</p>
      <a href="/educators" class="prog-educator-bridge__link">Flip the Script is built specifically for educators and school leaders →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- ── TIERS ── -->
<div class="prog-tiers-section" id="tiers">
  <div class="prog-tiers-inner">
    <div class="prog-reveal">
      <p class="prog-section-label">How deep do you want to dive?</p>
      <h2 class="prog-section-title">You'll meet the future<br><em>regardless</em>.</h2>
      <p class="prog-section-body">All three tiers get to peek into the future.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prog-tiers-grid prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s">

      <div class="prog-tier-card prog-tier-witness">
        <div class="prog-tier-name">Witness</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-tagline">Good — I'm interested</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-sessions">4</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-session-label">milestone sessions</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-time">Weeks 1 · 4 · 8 · 12 &nbsp;·&nbsp; ~3 hrs/week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-divider"></div>
        <ul class="prog-tier-gets">
          <li>Milestone moments of the journey</li>
          <li>Final ceremony &amp; Job Description reveal</li>
          <li>Access to session recordings</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact?tier=witness" class="prog-btn prog-btn-ghost prog-tier-btn">Perfect if your time is limited →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-tier-card prog-tier-traveler">
        <div class="prog-tier-name">Traveler</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-tagline">Better — I want the arc</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-sessions">8</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-session-label">sessions, every other week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-time">Alternating weeks &nbsp;·&nbsp; ~5–6 hrs/week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-divider"></div>
        <ul class="prog-tier-gets">
          <li>Full arc in compressed form</li>
          <li>Partial 2032 Job Description</li>
          <li>Beta feedback role</li>
          <li>Dyad partnerships</li>
          <li>Black Menagerie archetype practice</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact?tier=traveler" class="prog-btn prog-btn-ghost prog-tier-btn">The full story, every other chapter →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-tier-card prog-tier-questor">
        <div class="prog-tier-name">Questor</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-tagline">Best — I'm all in</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-sessions">12</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-session-label">sessions, full arc</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-time">Every week &nbsp;·&nbsp; ~7–8 hrs/week</div>
        <div class="prog-tier-divider"></div>
        <ul class="prog-tier-gets">
          <li>Complete 2032 Job Description</li>
          <li>Co-creator of the methodology</li>
          <li>Testimonial &amp; credit in future launches</li>
          <li>Morning pages + Artist Dates practice</li>
          <li>Full Black Menagerie archetype rotation</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact?tier=questor" class="prog-btn prog-btn-primary prog-tier-btn">Build new worlds from within →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- ── 12-WEEK JOURNEY ── -->
<div class="prog-journey-section" id="journey">
  <div class="prog-journey-inner">
    <div class="prog-reveal">
      <p class="prog-section-label">The Full Arc</p>
      <h2 class="prog-section-title">Every stage.<br><em>A question waiting.</em></h2>
      <p class="prog-section-body">12 weeks. 12 worlds. An arc that must be lived before it can be mapped.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prog-journey-flow prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.15s; margin-top:3rem;">

      <div class="prog-journey-phase prog-phase-descent">
        <div class="prog-journey-phase-header">
          <div>
            <div class="prog-phase-label">Phase I</div>
            <div class="prog-phase-name">Descent</div>
          </div>
          <div class="prog-phase-weeks">Weeks 1–4</div>
        </div>
        <ul class="prog-journey-stages">
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">01</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Status Quo</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">We meet you in your ordinary world. What does accepting the ordinary cost you?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">02</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Your Call to Adventure</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">Something stirs. A pull you've been ignoring. What have you been pretending not to hear?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">03</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Assistance</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">You look around and find you are not alone. Who shows up when you actually ask?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">04</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Departure</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">The familiar drops away. A journey toward your Future Self begins. What are you finally willing to let fall away?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-journey-phase prog-phase-crossing">
        <div class="prog-journey-phase-header">
          <div>
            <div class="prog-phase-label">Phase II</div>
            <div class="prog-phase-name">Crossing</div>
          </div>
          <div class="prog-phase-weeks">Weeks 5–8</div>
        </div>
        <ul class="prog-journey-stages">
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">05</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Trials</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">The road gets complicated. Old patterns show up in new costumes. What keeps finding you?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">06</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Approach</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">You get quiet. Go inward. What do you know that you haven't said out loud yet?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">07</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Crisis</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">The biggest thing. The one you've been circling. What would change if you stopped managing it?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">08</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Treasure</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">Something real surfaces. Hard-won and yours. What did you find that you weren't looking for?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-journey-phase prog-phase-emergence">
        <div class="prog-journey-phase-header">
          <div>
            <div class="prog-phase-label">Phase III</div>
            <div class="prog-phase-name">Emergence</div>
          </div>
          <div class="prog-phase-weeks">Weeks 9–12</div>
        </div>
        <ul class="prog-journey-stages">
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">09</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Result</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">The arc begins to show its shape. You look back. What looks different from here?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">10</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Return</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">The ordinary world again. Same address, different person. What can you see now that you couldn't before?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">11</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">New Life</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">A new chapter opens. Not because everything changed. Because you did. What are you ready to begin?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="prog-journey-stage">
            <div class="prog-stage-num">12</div>
            <div class="prog-stage-content">
              <div class="prog-stage-name">Resolution</div>
              <div class="prog-stage-prompt">A triumphant homecoming. The 2032 Job Description complete. What version of yourself just walked through the door?</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- CTA after reading the arc -->
    <div class="prog-journey-cta prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.25s">
      <p class="prog-journey-cta__text">Ready to begin your arc?</p>
      <a href="#waitlist" class="prog-btn prog-btn-primary">Reserve my spot in Cohort 02 →</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- ── TESTIMONIALS ── -->
<div class="prog-testimonials-section">
  <div class="prog-testimonials-inner">

    <blockquote class="prog-testimonial prog-reveal">
      <p class="prog-testimonial__quote">"She's not only listening to what you're saying verbally, but she's also listening to your tone, your word choice; she's able to develop a more well-informed understanding of your state and situation. Makēda has been an invaluable source of support for me."</p>
      <cite class="prog-testimonial__cite">Stephanie · building a music career</cite>
    </blockquote>

    <blockquote class="prog-testimonial prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.15s">
      <p class="prog-testimonial__quote">"By asking the right questions, providing the right tools, and being very supportive, Makēda helped me succeed in my academic studies, personal life, and with a difficult transition towards my professional life. Today I am much happier."</p>
      <cite class="prog-testimonial__cite">Etienne · navigating a life transition</cite>
    </blockquote>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- ── EARTH DAY / COHORT STATUS ── -->
<div class="prog-earthday-section prog-reveal">
  <div class="prog-earthday-stars" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="prog-earthday-inner">
    <div class="prog-earthday-globe" aria-hidden="true">🌍</div>
    <div class="prog-earthday-text">
      <p class="prog-earthday-eyebrow">Cohort 01 · Founding</p>
      <h2 class="prog-earthday-heading">Launched<br><em>Earth Day.</em></h2>
      <p class="prog-earthday-sub">The founding cohort is full and in motion.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="prog-divider"></div>

<!-- ── WAITLIST ── -->
<div class="prog-waitlist-section" id="waitlist">
  <div class="prog-waitlist-inner prog-reveal">

    <p class="prog-waitlist-eyebrow">Cohort 02 · Now Forming</p>
    <h2 class="prog-waitlist-heading">Your spot is waiting.</h2>
    <p class="prog-waitlist-body">Cohort 02 opens after the founding cohort completes. Add your name now. You'll be first through the door, before it opens publicly.</p>

    <form class="prog-waitlist-form" id="waitlistForm" name="cohort-02-waitlist" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="cohort-02-waitlist" />
      <input class="prog-waitlist-input" type="text" name="name" placeholder="your name" required />
      <input class="prog-waitlist-input" type="email" name="email" placeholder="your email" required />
      <textarea class="prog-waitlist-input prog-waitlist-textarea" name="navigating" rows="3" placeholder="what are you navigating right now?"></textarea>
      <button class="prog-btn prog-btn-primary prog-waitlist-submit" type="submit">Reserve my spot in Cohort 02 →</button>
    </form>

    <div class="prog-waitlist-confirm" id="waitlistConfirm" style="display:none;">
      <p class="prog-waitlist-confirm-msg">You're on the list. We'll find you when the portal opens. In the meantime, the Sandbox Sessions are open. Come play.</p>
      <a href="https://lu.ma/questlabs" class="prog-btn prog-btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Find a Sandbox Session →</a>
    </div>

    <p class="prog-waitlist-note">No commitment. Just your name at the threshold.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── CLOSING ── -->
<div class="prog-closing-section">
  <p class="prog-closing-quote prog-reveal">"We need every dream. Especially yours. Start where you are to get where we're going."</p>
  <p class="prog-closing-attr prog-reveal" style="transition-delay:0.15s">— Quest Labs</p>
</div>

<div class="page-bridge" style="max-width:860px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; padding-left:2.5rem; padding-right:2.5rem;">
  <p>Not ready for a full cohort?</p>
  <a href="https://lu.ma/questlabs" class="bridge-link">Start with a Sandbox Session, open door, donations based →</a>
  <a href="/educators" class="bridge-link" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">Leading a school or classroom? Flip the Script is for you →</a>
</div>

<footer>
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="footer-logo">Quest Labs</div>
      <div class="footer-tagline">Healing-Centered Futures</div>
    </div>
    <ul class="footer-links">
      <li><a href="/bet">Bet on Us</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-anchor">
    Not sure where to start?
    <a href="https://lu.ma/questlabs">Find a free Sandbox Session →</a>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-copy">2026 Quest Labs · Makēda · All futures reserved · Berlin &amp; Beyond</div>
</footer>

</div><!-- .prog-page -->

</Layout>

<script is:inline>
// ── WAITLIST FORM ──
const waitlistForm = document.getElementById('waitlistForm');
if (waitlistForm) {
  waitlistForm.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const data = new FormData(waitlistForm);
    await fetch('/', { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' }, body: new URLSearchParams(data).toString() });
    waitlistForm.style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('waitlistConfirm').style.display = 'block';
  });
}

// ── SCROLL REVEAL ──
const progReveals = document.querySelectorAll('.prog-reveal');
const progObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
  entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible'); });
}, { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });
progReveals.forEach(r => progObserver.observe(r));
</script>

<style is:global>
  /* ── WRAPPER ── */
  .prog-page {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ── BUTTONS ── */
  .prog-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
  }
  .prog-btn-primary {
    color: var(--text);
    background: var(--violet, #6B3FA0);
  }
  .prog-btn-primary:hover { background: var(--violet-mid, #8B5CC8); }
  .prog-btn-ghost {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    border: 0.5px solid rgba(139, 116, 171, 0.35);
    background: transparent;
  }
  .prog-btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: rgba(180, 143, 224, 0.6); }
  .cta-ghost {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    opacity: 0.55;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
  }
  .cta-ghost:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .prog-divider {
    height: 0.5px;
    background: var(--border-dim);
    margin: 0 2.5rem;
  }

  /* ── SECTION TYPOGRAPHY ── */
  .prog-section-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .prog-section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .prog-section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--violet-light, #B48FE0); }
  .prog-section-body {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .text-bright { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }

  /* ── REVEAL ANIMATION ── */
  .prog-reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .prog-reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .prog-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 88vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 6rem 2.5rem 4rem;
    max-width: 860px;
  }
  .prog-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(107, 63, 160, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .prog-hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.2s forwards;
  }
  .prog-hero-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 9rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: var(--gold-pale);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.35s forwards;
  }
  .prog-hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.5s forwards;
  }
  .prog-hero-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.65s forwards;
  }
  .prog-hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 0.8s forwards;
  }
  .prog-scroll-hint {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(240, 236, 248, 0.25);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: progFadeUp 0.8s ease 1s forwards;
  }
  .prog-scroll-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 0.5px;
    background: rgba(240, 236, 248, 0.2);
  }

  /* ── PREMISE ── */
  .prog-what-section {
    padding: 5rem 2.5rem;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .prog-educator-bridge {
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(107, 63, 160, 0.5);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    background: rgba(107, 63, 160, 0.05);
  }
  .prog-educator-bridge__label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #C4A8E8;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .prog-educator-bridge__link {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #C4A8E8;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .prog-educator-bridge__link:hover { color: #FDFCFA; }

  /* ── TIERS ── */
  .prog-tiers-section { padding: 5rem 2.5rem; }
  .prog-tiers-inner { max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .prog-tiers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .prog-tier-card {
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border-dim);
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
